  "id": "RAW_376a1b50",
  "title": "盘点 4 个让 AI Agent 变强的 Skills。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzUxNjg4NDEzNA==&mid=2247531723&idx=1&sn=b6e3ea8752e949cebac7de93692bbb4f",
  "date": "2026-03-01 07:05:00",
  "author": " 逛逛GitHub",
  "siteName": "逛逛GitHub",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f32e3009&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FM2ibDBMdECU3wZnggM7733PGcOEjys7wTQrJqicYEKCMoIBo7QFtrhd9Djg7mIv0206ZNRUdyjGs3fOkQL7ZnLibIrSIz1I6OKEpcN2ibdicXicsw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <div style=\"padding: 20px 15px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;color: #333;background-color: #fff;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlwhi7fj9mz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div>\n    <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-profile class=\"js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"逛逛GitHub\" data-alias=\"ggGithub\" data-from=\"0\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/ePw3ZeGRruyXo8VzACicO8MVibibicuJUQ8Vzghx6WF8F51breYjBIuYd4cj6wp26BYrg850bNuA20rdic9UyKIUhpg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"热门「开源项目」推送到你眼前，每日为你节省 1 小时。 给我发消息可咨询各种开源项目，专注 AI、硬科技开源领域。\" data-id=\"MzUxNjg4NDEzNA==\" data-is_biz_ban=\"0\" data-service_type=\"1\" data-verify_status=\"0\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:32px;font-family:Futura-Medium;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlzw9ifnz5e\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlzw9ifzztw\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">01</span></span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;margin-top: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Vercel 官方的 Skills 搜索神器</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfuteja\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Skills 这么多，怎么找到适合自己的？ &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfuteja\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Vercel 官方出了个 find-skills，专门解决这个问题。它本质上是一个 Skills 包管理器，通过&nbsp;</span><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfute1a41\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(214, 51, 132);\"><span leaf=\"\">npx skills</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;命令就能用。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100047912\" data-ratio=\"0.5064814814814815\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1bed5824&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM2ibDBMdECU1MEL4JnE7Nz0OLpsiaARq3fiamfZpw3JBRJOPpWOdMJpFImia9KSuyOxLBQRn6ve1WtsMdxza1f0SEnSVic7LuVYKbyaPugl8U3Tk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfute1ywh\"><span leaf=\"\">核心功能挺直接的：</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfute9ak\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(214, 51, 132);\"><span leaf=\"\">npx skills find [关键词]</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;搜索 Skills，支持交互式搜索 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfute99e\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(214, 51, 132);\"><span leaf=\"\">npx skills add &lt;包名&gt;</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;安装 Skill &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfuteu4f\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(214, 51, 132);\"><span leaf=\"\">npx skills check</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;检查更新 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfutel14\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(214, 51, 132);\"><span leaf=\"\">npx skills update</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;一键更新所有已安装的 Skills &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfute1z3u\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">比如你想找 React 性能优化相关的 Skill，直接运行&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(214, 51, 132);\"><span leaf=\"\">npx skills find react performance</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，它会列出所有相关的 Skills，还会给你安装命令和文档链接。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfute1z3u\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">官方还做了一个 Skills 搜索网站&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">skills.sh</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，可以在线浏览所有的 Skills。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhfute1t0w\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">对于经常用 AI Agent 干活的人来说，这个工具能帮你快速发现和安装各种能力扩展，省得到处找。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span leaf=\"\">开源地址：<span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">https</span>:<span class=\"code-snippet__comment\">//github.com/vercel-labs/skills/blob/main/skills/find-skills/SKILL.md</span></span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"padding: 20px 15px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;color: #333;background-color: #fff;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlwhi7fj9mz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlzwal251goo\" style=\"font-size: 32px;font-family: Futura-Medium;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlzwal2f1hey\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">02</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic 官方的 Skill 创建指南 &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggajxv8\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">如果你想自己写一个 Skill，这个官方指南是必看的。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggaj1xjp\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Anthropic 作为 Claude 的出品方，他们出的 skill-creator 可以说是权威教程。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5324074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100047913\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=534412f1&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM2ibDBMdECU3KhjTgng5aShxL44yjKeMHQKZ9ic6uoNvicHtEFLUqnZ3iauGGHiarQrzekic9jDkL0OGibgQh2K8FLNibTDkH7hpSQ80bWPgLicmaKTA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:16px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggaj146w\"><span leaf=\"\">它把 Skill 的结构讲得很清楚：</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggajfct\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">SKILL.md</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;是核心文件，包含 YAML 元数据和 Markdown 指令 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggaj1y15\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">scripts/</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;放可执行脚本 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggajrf9\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">references/</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;放参考文档 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 20px;margin:0px 0px 8px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggaj200v\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">assets/</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;放模板、图片等资源文件 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggaj47j\"><span leaf=\"\">比较有价值的几个设计原则：</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggaj2006\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">渐进式加载</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：Skill 分三层加载，先是元数据（约100词），再是 SKILL.md 主体（&lt;5k词），最后按需加载引用文件。这样设计是为了省上下文窗口。 &nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggaj1n83\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">自由度匹配</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：任务越脆弱，指令越具体；任务越灵活，指令越宽松。就像走钢丝需要护栏，在广场上可以随便走。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggaj1wag\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">不要创建多余文件</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：Skill 不需要 README.md、安装指南、更新日志这些，它只需要 AI 干活要用的信息。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhggajvrs\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">整个指南非常实用，从理解需求、规划内容、初始化、编写到打包发布，每个步骤都有详细说明。想认真做 Skill 的话，这个值得好好读一遍。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"ruby\"><code><span leaf=\"\">开源地址：<span class=\"code-snippet__symbol\">https:</span>/<span class=\"code-snippet__regexp\">/github.com/anthropics/skills/blob/main/skills/skill-creator/</span><span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">SKILL</span>.md</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"padding: 20px 15px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;color: #333;background-color: #fff;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlwhi7fj9mz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <mpcpc class=\"js_cpc_area res_iframe cpc_iframe\" data-category_id_list=\"5|6|17|21|41|43|48|59\" js_editor_cpcad=\"\" src=\"/cgi-bin/readtemplate?t=tmpl/cpc_tmpl#1771894996942\" data-id=\"1771894996942\"></mpcpc>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlzwc6vq16ux\" style=\"font-size: 32px;font-family: Futura-Medium;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlzwc6w6mbf\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">03</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 24px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">强制设计的 Brainstorming Skill &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhhcf11fp6\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这个 Skill 有点意思，它强制你在动手写代码之前先做设计。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhhcf1sb1\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">它的核心理念是：<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">任何项目，不管多简单，都必须先经过设计讨论，获得你认可后才能开始实现。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5370370370370371\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100047914\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d63b03fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM2ibDBMdECU3DTz3s53DIkGFtjREgjgNZzxpUDyBPcrjc19rAC8EApKVXfHOLY9zSsPYib9iaqZGWGM8S8Ad2goIgtAwnBz4k7ypyZbe9zjEFA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhhcf1d4c\"><span leaf=\"\">整个过程分几步：</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhhcf123l9\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">先了解项目上下文，看看文件、文档、最近的提交。然后一个一个问题问清楚，搞明白目的、约束和成功标准。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhhcf11866\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">接下来提出 2-3 个方案，说明各自的优缺点，给出你的推荐理由。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhhcf11z86\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">最后呈现设计，按模块逐步展示，每个模块确认没问题再往下走。设计通过后，写一份设计文档保存到&nbsp;</span><span style=\"border-radius:4px;padding:2px 6px;color:rgb(214, 51, 132);\"><span leaf=\"\">docs/plans/</span></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;目录，然后才能调用实现相关的 Skill。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhhcf1ow2\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">有个硬性规定</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：在用户批准设计之前，禁止调用任何实现类 Skill，禁止写代码，禁止搭建项目。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhhcf1v2j\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">听起来有点繁琐，但实际上能避免很多返工。很多时候我们觉得简单的项目，做着做着就发现各种问题，还不如一开始就把事情想清楚。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"ruby\"><code><span leaf=\"\">开源地址：<span class=\"code-snippet__symbol\">https:</span>/<span class=\"code-snippet__regexp\">/github.com/obra/superpowers/blob/main/skills/brainstorming/</span><span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">SKILL</span>.md</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"padding: 20px 15px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;color: #333;background-color: #fff;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlwhi7fj9mz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlzwd1jz1twf\" style=\"font-size: 32px;font-family: Futura-Medium;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlzwd1kg145t\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">04</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-weight:bold;font-size:16px;\"><span leaf=\"\">系统化调试的 Debugging Skill</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f817h4\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个 Skill 是给 AI 用的调试方法论，核心原则就一句话：</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">没有找到根本原因之前，禁止尝试任何修复</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6398148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100047915\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=120b6bb0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FM2ibDBMdECU1JnqUIibokPTqibMVmIicDjI5BjsY0VOFYC4FRvBfGZeH0SlDWL7cmwYPafDeKfJiaOmia1yb2aicvtT9WpibRfMjMwp1LicqgwKshZVU%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;font-size:14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f8qp8\"><span leaf=\"\">它把调试过程分成四个阶段：</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f8lr\"><span leaf=\"\">阶段一：根因调查</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f81io2\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">仔细读错误信息，可靠地复现问题，检查最近的改动。如果是多组件系统，还要在每个组件边界加诊断日志，搞清楚数据在哪儿断的。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f814np\"><span leaf=\"\">阶段二：模式分析</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f81fzj\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">找类似的工作代码，对比差异，理解依赖关系。不要想当然地觉得某些差异不相关。&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f88tl\"><span leaf=\"\">阶段三：假设和测试</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f8b6d\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">提出单一假设，用最小改动去测试。一次只改一个变量，不要一次性修多个问题。如果不对，回到阶段一重新分析。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;font-size: 14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f8ihv\"><span leaf=\"\">阶段四：实现</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px 0px 16px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f8lje\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">先写失败的测试用例，然后修复根因，最后验证修复有效。如果连续 3 次修复都失败，停下来质疑架构设计。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <p style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-size:16px;line-height:2em;text-align:left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mlwhi7f81d8t\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个方法论的好处是避免乱猜乱试，减少改出一个 Bug 引出两个新 Bug 的情况。</span><strong style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">据统计，系统化调试 15-30 分钟搞定，随机修复可能要折腾 2-3 小时</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n  <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n  <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"ruby\"><code><span leaf=\"\">开源地址：<span class=\"code-snippet__symbol\">https:</span>/<span class=\"code-snippet__regexp\">/github.com/obra/superpowers/blob/main/skills/systematic-debugging/</span><span class=\"code-snippet__variable\">SKILL</span>.md</span></code></pre>\n  <p></p>\n  <div style=\"padding: 20px 15px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 1.8;color: #333;background-color: #fff;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei UI', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mlwhi7fj9mz\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p class=\"js_darkmode__32\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:24px 8px 0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;